<!-- 
Usefull scaling steps to use for individual sclaing presets in 1/16 increments for better scaling. (1/8 steps are also usable):

EXAMPLE INCREMENTS:
0.6875   (11/16)  ultra small
0.75     (12/16)  very safe
0.8125   (13/16)
0.875    (14/16)
0.9375   (15/16)
1.0      (16/16)
1.125    (18/16)
1.25     (20/16)
1.375    (22/16)

VANILA:
0.88  MonitorSmall          
1     MonitorMedium            
1.125 MonitorBig             
1.25  TelevisionSmall       
1.375 TelevisionMedium  
1.5   TelevisionBig              

Change according to your own needs :)
-->



<ModOps>
  <ModOp Type="merge" GUID="50286" Path="Values/UIConfigScaling/Scalings">
    <Scalings>
      <MonitorSmall><Value>0.6875</Value></MonitorSmall>
      <MonitorMedium><Value>0.8125</Value></MonitorMedium>
      <MonitorBig><Value>1.000</Value></MonitorBig>
      <TelevisionSmall><Value>1.125</Value></TelevisionSmall>
      <TelevisionMedium><Value>1.25</Value></TelevisionMedium>
      <TelevisionBig><Value>1.375</Value></TelevisionBig>
    </Scalings>
  </ModOp>
</ModOps>